sequenceDiagram
    title Orchestrated ingest loop — analyze once, retry generate, bounded (I7)
    autonumber

    participant O as Orchestrator
    participant P as InferenceProvider (Local/API)
    participant V as WikiPage validator
    participant U as Usage accumulator
    participant FS as Wiki FS
    participant PG as Postgres

    Note over O: max_iter=3, token_budget=60000 (from provider_config, ADR-0009)
    O->>P: analyze(source_text, vault_context)  %% ONCE per run (AQ-v0.2-1)
    P-->>O: Analysis{topics, entities, language, suggested_pages}
    P->>U: add Usage(input, output, cost)

    loop iteration = 1..max_iter  (stop when converged OR iteration==max_iter OR tokens>=budget)
        Note over O: check token_budget BEFORE the call — if accumulated >= budget, stop converged=False
        O->>P: generate(analysis, retrieval_context + augmentation)
        P-->>O: list[WikiPage]
        P->>U: add Usage(input, output, cost)
        O->>V: validate(pages)  %% type∈enum, title, non-empty sources[], lang, content (ADR-0007 §5)
        alt all pages valid
            V-->>O: OK (converged=True)
            O->>FS: write each WikiPage to wiki/ (I1 upsert, I5 frontmatter)
            O->>PG: persist_metadata + parse links (K5) + upsert vector
            Note over O: break out of loop
        else invalid (whole batch retried)
            V-->>O: errors[]
            Note over O: augment retrieval_context with validation errors; iteration += 1
        end
    end

    Note over O: if loop ended without converging → converged=False (AC-K2-5)
    O->>U: finalize → total_tokens, total_cost_usd
    O->>PG: INSERT ingest_runs{max_iter_used, total_tokens, total_cost_usd, converged} (I7)
    Note over O: log total_cost_usd; if > $1.00 → WARNING + cost_anomaly=True (ADR-0009)
